description: Kat (0-1 lifetime) takes on the gifted Spider (3-2 lifetime). Kat is a hellion but just no match for the bigger stronger Spider. You have to give props to Kat. She never quits, fighting till the end even when she realizes there is not much she could do. The Spider plays with Kat, like she's a kitten, trying out new moves and holds on her. At the end of the day The Spider has her prize, and defiantly turns the humiliation up a notch for rd 4.
title: The Spider vs. Kat
